title: Women Around the World: Abisoye Ajayi Akinfolarin
itunes:title: Women Around the World: Abisoye Ajayi Akinfolarin
description:
By establishing her NGO Pearls Africa Foundation, Abisoye Ajayi Akinfolarin has provided numerous girls access to training in technology among other things, and has worked tirelessly to close the technological gender gap in her community.
